# Instance-level private working artifacts.
# These contain rough living notes whose value depends on being unpolished.
# See ../methodology.md#publicprivate-posture for the file-status discipline.

# Parking lot — living learning notes; would lose value if sanitized for a reader.
parking-lot.md

# Operator profile — instance-specific calibration with personal positioning + pace data.
# Sanitized templates for forkers belong in framework/, not here.
operator-profile.md

# Monthly retrospectives — honest personal reflection content; "no state lies" is harder when written for a reader.
retrospectives/
